title: Change Your Life Forever - Hypnosis
description:
Save the files on your iPod and use earphones when you listen to them.

Listen to the files in the folder Daily A before you sleep everyday for 30 days.  
It is perfectly fine if you fall asleep while listening to them.
That's the idea, listening to them while you sleep saves you a lot of time.

Repeat the process with the folder Daily B for the next month.

This will forever change your life.  I promise!!!  

Please seed if you are interested in changing your life 
and the lives of others in this world.  

Peace
